For the newcomers asking what is a pump!

▶️▶️What is a pump ?◀️◀️👇

A pump happens when a coin is bought for a big amount in a short period of time, making the coin price to explode.

How 🤷‍♀️ will a pump happen ?👇

We will choose a specific date and time for the pump to take place and when that time comes we will write the name of the coin on this group so that everyone will start buying. 
⏰We will try to hold the coin pumping for at least 3 minutes and then start selling it in stages, not to ruin the chances of the others.
🚅The chosen coin will top the list of the highest sold coins, and it will attract strangers and bots to buy it, and this is how we will have a successful pump every time.
